= medusa - The terminology manager for perseus-a

== VERSION

This documentation refers to medusa version 0.0.1


== DESCRIPTION

TODO: well, the description... ;-)

Developed at "prometheus - Das verteilte digitale Bildarchiv für Forschung
und Lehre" (Institute for Art History, University of Cologne, Germany), during
the project "perseus-a - Automatische Erschließung des prometheus-Bildarchivs"
("Automatic indexing for the prometheus image archive"), funded by the
RheinEnergieStiftung Cologne, Germany.


